Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:45.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.53,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.87,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:56.04,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:08.83,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}话不投机 有些后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:10.78,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:16.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}心随着急切的情感变乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:23.42,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}调整情绪 想知道真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:29.17,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}执着于达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.85,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不觉间模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:38.57,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天是崭新的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:44.00,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.60,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.94,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:55.03,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:58.66,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}一毫米的距离也觉得遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.73,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}匆匆走过的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:06.00,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}不会忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.76,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下闪耀的一页
